const NAV=[{id:"dashboard",ic:"📊",lb:"Dashboard"},{id:"pos",ic:"🛒",lb:"POS Billing"},{id:"products",ic:"📦",lb:"Products"},{id:"customers",ic:"👥",lb:"Customers"},{id:"orders",ic:"📋",lb:"Orders"},{id:"bills",ic:"🧾",lb:"Bills"},{id:"inventory",ic:"🗃️",lb:"Inventory"},{id:"purchases",ic:"🚚",lb:"Purchases"},{id:"reports",ic:"📈",lb:"Reports"},{id:"settings",ic:"⚙️",lb:"Settings"}];
